data.description:
Welcome to this captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that invites you to experience a harmonious blend of modern aesthetics with classic appeal. Step inside to find a stylish and spacious interior, adorned with 12x24 tiles that grace the floors of the living areas. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it perfect for both daily living and entertaining guests.The well-crafted kitchen is the focal point of this home, showcasing wood cabinets that offer abundant storage space. With sleek countertops and contemporary appliances, it's a haven for any culinary enthusiast. Three bedrooms ensure ample space for your family or guests. The master bedroom comes complete with an en-suite bathroom for added convenience and privacy. Step outside to discover a sprawling yard, providing an ideal canvas for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply soaking in the Arizona sun. The fully fenced lot ensures security, making it a haven for pets and children to play freely. This property isn't just a pretty face; it's practical too, with a tile roof that adds durability and enhances its Southwestern charm.

Conveniently located, offering easy access to local schools, parks, shopping centers, dining options, and major transportation routes. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or seeking an upgrade, this home offers a unique blend of comfort and convenience that Tucson residents love. Your next chapter starts here!
